---
import Logo from "./Logo.astro";
import { sitePath } from "../lib/paths";
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="shell footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-intro">
      <Logo />
      <p>沿着算力与价值链理解 AI 产业，用可追溯信息辅助独立判断。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <div>
        <strong>浏览</strong>
        <a href={sitePath("/map/")}>产业地图</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/companies/")}>公司目录</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/news/")}>权威情报</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/research/")}>研究主题</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/updates/")}>数据更新</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>关于</strong>
        <a href={sitePath("/methodology/")}>方法与来源</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/updates/")}>数据管线</a>
        <a href={sitePath("/exports/atlas.json")}>AI 数据导出</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="shell footer-bottom">
    <p>本站内容仅用于信息整理与学习，不构成投资建议。市场有风险，决策需独立。</p>
    <span>© 2026 智芯图谱 AI & Silicon Atlas</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin-top: 7rem;
    padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  }

  .footer-intro p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin: 1.3rem 0 0;
    max-width: 24rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(7rem, 1fr));
  }

  .footer-links div {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .footer-links strong {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--mint);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    display: flex;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .footer-links {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
